Assistant-Surgeon Thomas Seward, M.D., from 59th Foot, vice Charles Healy, who exchanges. Dated 16th March, 1870.

Assistant-Surgeon Edward Denham Tomlinson, from the Military Train. Dated 16th March, 1870.

